data.description: Charming Ranch Style Brick Home in Brynn Marr Subdivision!Welcome to your new home! Nestled in a cul-de-sac, this delightful ranch-style brick residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Boasting a spacious layout, this property features:3 cozy bedrooms, providing ample space for your family and guests.2 modern baths, elegantly designed for your comfort and convenience.A fenced yard, perfect for enjoying outdoor activities in privacy and security. New paint throughout, creating a fresh and inviting ambiance for your enjoyment.New flooring, enhancing the aesthetic appeal and adding a touch of contemporary style.New stainless steel appliances, making cooking and entertaining a delightful experience.A stylish kitchen island, providing extra space for meal preparation and casual dining.Conveniently located close to shopping centers, schools, parks, and all major amenities, this inviting property presents an ideal opportunity to settle into a comfortable and well-connected neighborhood. Don't miss the chance to make this house your home! Schedule a viewing today!
